location.fullValue: The Redwood II - Slab Foundation Plan, Old Hawthorne Estates

data.description: Better Than New!!! The Villas at Old Hawthorne.  4-sides brick, 1.5 Story with 3-car garage. ~2818 SQFT.  4 Large Bedrooms, 3 Full Bathrooms, Spacious Living Room, Kitchen, Dining Room combination with wood flooring, gas fireplace, gas cooktop, wall oven, granite countertops, island, and walk-in pantry.  Other features include temperature-controlled storage area, spacious upstairs bedroom suite/ office space, closet organizers, ceiling fans, screened patio, gas fireplace, walk-in primary shower, high efficiency HVAC with humidifier.  Upgrades include New Roof, Water Softener, Security System, and Roman Shades. Irrigation system, landscaping, and snow removal are maintained by the Association.  A must see and move-in ready.
